  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Datafeed Archiving: Usage Log with DATAFDLOG</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page concept  - topic-topic concept-concept \" id=\"loio4ea2fda859b74f56e10000000a42189e\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Datafeed Archiving: Usage Log with DATAFDLOG</h1><div class=\"body conbody\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n\n<p class=\"p\">When the user log is archived, the data is written to an external file. </p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Activities\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Activities</h2>\n\n<ol class=\"ol\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Financial Supply Chain Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Treasury and Risk Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Basic Functions</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Market Data Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Datafeed</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Usage Log</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Archive</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span>.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Archive Administration: Generate Archive Files</span> screen appears. </p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Enter the variant needed to start the archiving program, the start date, and the spool parameters. </p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Create Job</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> to start the archiving. </p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">You can do the following: </p><ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"4ea2c6995a2f4f57e10000000a42189e.html\">Reload the archive</a>\n</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"4ea2c6c65a2f4f57e10000000a42189e.html\">Manage the archive</a>\n</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"4ea2c6615a2f4f57e10000000a42189e.html\">Read the archive</a>\n</p></li>\n</ul></li>\n</ol>\n</section></div>\n</div><div class=\"related-links\"> </div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
